stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft

    Draft --> Sent: send invoice
    Draft --> Cancelled: cancel invoice

    Sent --> PartiallyPaid: receive partial payment
    Sent --> Paid: receive full payment
    Sent --> Overdue: due date passes
    Sent --> Cancelled: cancel invoice

    PartiallyPaid --> Paid: receive final payment
    PartiallyPaid --> Overdue: due date passes (remaining)
    PartiallyPaid --> Cancelled: cancel invoice

    Overdue --> PartiallyPaid: receive partial payment
    Overdue --> Paid: receive full payment
    Overdue --> Cancelled: cancel invoice

    Paid --> [*]
    Cancelled --> [*]